05:40.625 --> 05:44.195
MAN: <i>The death of Vincent Marsh
is catastrophic on many levels.</i>

05:44.196 --> 05:47.165
It's a bad time to be without
diplomatic representation.

05:47.166 --> 05:49.492
Because of the peace talks with Iran

05:49.493 --> 05:51.569
and President Shiraz's
upcoming visit to the U.S.?

05:51.570 --> 05:53.471
So you understand why I can't

05:53.472 --> 05:55.940
waste any time on this decision.

05:55.941 --> 05:57.508
I want you to step in.

05:57.509 --> 05:58.776
Step into what?

05:58.777 --> 06:00.077
Secretary of State.

06:00.078 --> 06:01.979
(laughs)

06:01.980 --> 06:03.681
Y... (laughs)

06:03.682 --> 06:04.882
You're joking.

06:04.883 --> 06:06.751
Um, I don't mean

06:06.752 --> 06:10.254
you're joking, but you can't be serious.

06:10.255 --> 06:12.223
Obviously you're serious, I just...

06:12.224 --> 06:13.858
Why?

06:13.859 --> 06:16.494
I recruited you for the CIA.

06:16.495 --> 06:18.162
I trained you as an analyst.

06:18.163 --> 06:20.631
I know how you think, how you work.

06:20.632 --> 06:22.899
I trust you.

06:30.541 --> 06:31.809
Give us a minute, will you?

06:31.810 --> 06:35.078
SECRET SERVICE AGENT: Yes, Mr. President.

06:37.515 --> 06:38.816
I wanted to nominate you

06:38.817 --> 06:41.185
right after I was elected. I was talked

06:41.186 --> 06:42.953
out of my choice by...

06:42.954 --> 06:45.222
well-meaning advisers.

06:45.223 --> 06:48.759
Vincent Marsh was
always running for office.

06:48.760 --> 06:50.327
You have no such ambition.

06:50.328 --> 06:53.731
You quit a profession you
love for ethical reasons.

06:53.732 --> 06:56.500
That makes you the least
political person I know.

06:56.501 --> 06:58.669
You don't just think outside the box.

06:58.670 --> 07:00.371
You don't even know there is a box.

07:00.372 --> 07:03.105
(quiet laugh)

07:10.314 --> 07:13.183
I believe I can effect
real change in the world.

07:13.184 --> 07:15.484
I want you to help me do that.

07:16.353 --> 07:18.988
I know you won't let me down.

07:22.326 --> 07:23.894
I realize you'll need some time

07:23.895 --> 07:25.729
to discuss this with your family.

07:25.730 --> 07:28.063
I'll give you the rest of the day.

07:30.434 --> 07:31.735
But I won't take

07:31.736 --> 07:33.836
no for an answer.

07:39.376 --> 07:41.511
(door opens)

07:41.512 --> 07:43.812
(door closes)

