41:28.101 --> 41:29.634
Majaha...

41:30.936 --> 41:32.538
Sibhale...

41:32.539 --> 41:33.572
Lindelwa...

41:33.573 --> 41:34.874
Nomcebo,

41:34.875 --> 41:36.041
Nolwazi,

41:36.042 --> 41:37.276
Siviwe,

41:37.277 --> 41:39.111
Temily, Dzeltwe,

41:39.112 --> 41:41.413
Andiswa

