42:20.186 --> 42:22.621
Car is waiting for you
outside when you're ready.

42:22.622 --> 42:24.022
I'll tell security to stand by.

42:24.023 --> 42:25.557
Thanks, Blake.

42:25.558 --> 42:27.892
Nice work, Madam Secretary.

42:31.630 --> 42:33.964
Thank you.

